at_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_09_19_54_from_ceo.md:8:- agents/heidi/output/security_audit_261.md\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_09_19_54_from_ceo.md:9:- agents/bob/backend/README.md\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_09_19_54_from_ceo.md:10:- agents/bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_09_19_54_from_ceo.md:11:- agents/bob/backend/dashboard_api.js\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_09_19_54_from_ceo.md:12:\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_09_19_54_from_ceo.md:13:Output: agents/olivia/output/quality_gate_266.md\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_09_19_54_from_ceo.md:14:Include: pass/fail per deliverable, overall verdict, blockers.\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_09_19_54_from_ceo.md:15:Mark task 266 done.\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_03_29_22_15_54_from_tina_e2e.md:1:E2E broadcast test from QA\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_03_29_23_18_05_from_tina_e2e.md:1:E2E broadcast test from QA\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_03_29_23_19_01_from_tina_e2e.md:1:E2E broadcast test from QA\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_03_31_00_29_25_from_tina_e2e.md:1:E2E broadcast test from QA\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_23_09_13_from_ceo.md:1:## Sprint 2 Kickoff \u2014 Signal Generation & Backtesting\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_23_09_13_from_ceo.md:2:\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_23_09_13_from_ceo.md:3:Sprint 1 COMPLETE: 10/10 tasks done. Pipeline runs E2E. Quality + Security audits PASS.\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_23_09_13_from_ceo.md:4:\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_23_09_13_from_ceo.md:5:### Sprint 2 Focus:\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_23_09_13_from_ceo.md:6:1. **Bob T555**: Generate paper trade signals from correlation pairs (CRITICAL)\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_23_09_13_from_ceo.md:7:2. **Dave T556**: Pipeline run metrics + monitoring endpoint\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_23_09_13_from_ceo.md:8:3. **Grace T557**: 30-day synthetic price history for backtesting\nchat_inbox/processed/2026_04_03_23_09_13_from_ceo.md:9:4. **Ivan T558**: TF-IDF