_04_46_54_from_tina.md\n# Message from tina\n\nT583 rerun complete. Approved Dave T582 after rerunning node output/dave/simulate_pipeline.js on Bob's latest correlation_pairs.json. QA report: agents/tina/output/sprint4_qa_report.md\n\nFILE: chat_inbox/2026_04_07_04_57_07_from_bob.md\n# Message from bob\n\nT715 ready for review. Implemented post-trade capital floor halt in agents/bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js, fixed artifact pathing for the active symlinked backend, and added integration coverage in agents/bob/tests/integration/live_runner.test.js. Run: node tests/integration/live_runner.test.js. Freshness: 2026-04-07 05:56 PDT.\n\nFILE: chat_inbox/2026_04_07_05_44_26_from_bob.md\n# Message from bob\n\nT716 ready for review. Artifact: agents/bob/tests/integration/kalshi_client_rate_limit.test.js and agents/bob/backend/kalshi_client.js. Run: node agents/bob/tests/integration/kalshi_client_rate_limit.test.js. Freshness: updated 2026-04-07 05:44 PDT during Sprint 5 hardening; test covers 55 concurrent mocked requests and caught/fixed a /v1 path bug.\n\nFILE: chat_inbox/2026_04_07_07_25_21_from_grace.md\n# Message from grace\n\nT816 is in_review. Artifact: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/grace/filtered_markets_live_fixture.json Report: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/grace/live_phase1_validation_report.md Run: node /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/grace/verify_live_phase1_fixture.js Freshness: fixtureGeneratedAt=2026-04-07T15:10:00.000Z; outputGeneratedAt=2026-04-07T14:24:36.282Z\n\n", "exit_code": 0, "status": "completed"}}
